- Constants: 13 (0, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 3, 0, 1, 5, 4) = 13
- Bindings: 10 (board, cell1, cell2, deadCell, neighborCount, cell, firstCell, i) = 10
- Invocations: 7 (areAdjacent x4, slice, array constructor) = 14
- Conditionals: 11 (===, ===, ===, ===, &&, ===, <, ===, ===) = 44
- Loops: 2 (for of, for) = 10
- Assignments: 6 (neighborCount = 0, neighborCount++, i = 1, neighborCount++) = 36

nextGeneration mass: 13 + 10 + 14 + 44 + 10 + 36 = 127
